    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Yyou apply your wit to control the field of battle as well as social interactions. You can use your Intelligence modifier in place of your Charisma modifier for all your Warlord features, and you also gain the following benefits.</p><p><strong>Bonus Skill and Language.</strong> You gain proficiency in one of the following skills of your choice: Arcana, History, Investigation, Nature, Religion; and a language of your choice.</p><p><strong>Intelligence Test.</strong> You can use your Intelligence modifier instead of your Wisdom modifier or Charisma modifier when making Wisdom or Charisma checks. You may do this a number of times equal to your Proficiency Bonus per Long Rest.</p><p><strong>Tactical Mastery.</strong> You can use the mastery propery of one additional simple weapon and one martial weapon.  The number of additional mastery properties you can use increases at Warlord levels 7 (2 simple, 2 martial), and 11 (3 simple, 3 martial).</p>",
